caption.p: Effect of carvacrol and thymol combination in cell death induction through apoptotic and cell stress pathways. Western blot (WB) of caspase-3, caspase-9, CHOP, PI3k, pAKT, and B actin expression following carvacrol and thymol treatment (individually or in combination). A representative figure of WB results from three independent experiments is presented.
